WEAKNESSES
  Cold (x2 damage)
    Alchemical fluids crystallize. Copper contracts and becomes brittle.
    Joints seize. The animation medium fractures.

  Lightning (x2 damage + ARC)
    Copper-plated. Electricity arcs through the entire frame. If two or
    more False Draugr are within 10 feet of each other when one takes
