ATTACK PHILOSOPHY
  Everything about their offense is designed to DISABLE, not kill.

  The Alchemical Blade deals low damage (6) but stacks Chemical Burns
  and Numbness. Each -2 Agility from Numbness makes it progressively
  harder to escape the NEXT Breaker's Restraining Grapple. They are a
  team debuff machine — the first one softens you, the second one pins
  you, the third one Breaker's Blows you while you're held.

  They have NO ranged attacks. No AoE. No frost breath. Purely contact-
  based threats. If you are not within arm's reach, you are safe. This
  is the inverse of Draugr Sentinels, who can frost-breathe a 15-foot
  cone at range.


