SECTION 6: HOW THE PARTY WINS


THE PARTY'S ANTI-DRAUGR PLAYBOOK (DOES NOT WORK)

  Fire:              Immune. Does nothing.
  Turn Undead:       No effect. They are not undead.
  Detect Undead:     Returns nothing. They are not undead.
  Detect Life:       Returns nothing. They are not alive.
  Sneaking past:     Fails. Tremorsense auto-detects movement.
  Holy magic:        No effect. No soul, no spiritual bond to disrupt.
  Standard melee:    Works, but alchemical regeneration heals 3/round.
                     An uphill grind without elemental support.


WHAT ACTUALLY WORKS

  Cold damage:       x2 damage AND suppresses regeneration. Frost spells,
                     GLACIES potions, Frost Salts thrown at them, cold
                     environments. The fluids crystallize, the copper
                     becomes brittle, the joints seize.

  Lightning damage:  x2 damage AND suppresses regeneration AND arcs to
                     adjacent Breakers for half damage. Shock spells,
                     FULGUR compounds, Void Salts. The copper frame
                     conducts the full charge.

  Sonic / Thunder:   Staggered 1 round. The resonance flaw from Ulag.
                     Orion's War Horn. A sustained note at the right
                     frequency. Buys time, doesn't deal damage.

  Invisibility:      Full effect. CAECITAS potions, Invisibility spells.
                     Walk right past them.

  Standing still:    They lose you. Freeze in place and they return to
                     patrol. Requires discipline under pressure.

  Getting airborne:  Levitation, being carried, standing on furniture.
                     Removes weight from the floor, removes detection.

  VITALIS (healing   Pouring a healing potion on them deals the potion's
  potions as weapon): HP value as damage, ignoring DR. The alchemy system
                     mastery reward.

  Called shots to    Hard Agility (-4). Disable a limb — removes grapple
  joints:            capability (arm) or movement (leg). They are
                     mechanical, not spiritual. Unlike true Draugr, whose
                     animation is holistic, their joints are physical
                     linkages that can be severed.

  Observing the      Forfeit a turn to watch a specific Breaker. Gain
  script:            Advantage on the next action against it. They are
                     predictable because they cannot adapt.


